%H A124696 Stephan Mertens, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2408.08053">Domination Polynomials of the Grid, the Cylinder, the Torus, and the King Graph</a>, arXiv:2408.08053 [math.CO], 2024. See p. 5.
